OL,3,CCharity Commission launches inquiry
OL,4,Cinto Presbyterian Church
OL,6,FThe Charity Commission has launched a
OL,7,Fstatutory inquiry into the
OL,8,FPresbyterian Church in Ireland.
OL,10,FIt comes after a review found "serious
OL,11,Fand significant failings" in the
OL,12,Fchurch's safeguarding functions from
OL,13,F2009 to 2022.
OL,15,FThe commission said it will work with
OL,16,Fthe church to ensure the issues
OL,17,Fidentified are addressed and
OL,18,F"appropriate remedial steps are put in
OL,19,Fplace".
