OL,3,CCharity Commission launches inquiry
OL,4,Cinto Presbyterian Church
OL,6,FIt emerged that failures included
OL,7,Fsituations where the church did not
OL,8,Frespond when people who had suffered
OL,9,Fharm sought help and instances where
OL,10,Foffenders returned to worship in
OL,11,Fchurch but were "inadequately
OL,12,Fmonitored".
OL,14,FA police investigation remains active.
OL,16,FThe church is set to hold a special
OL,17,Fgeneral assembly later this week.
