OL,3,CCharity Commission launches inquiry
OL,4,Cinto Presbyterian Church
OL,6,FThe Presbyterian Church in Ireland is
OL,7,Fa registered charity and the Charity
OL,8,FCommission has a legal responsibility
OL,9,Fto investigate misconduct or
OL,10,Fmismanagement.
OL,12,FAn inquiry is the commission's highest
OL,13,Flevel of investigation, which it said
OL,14,F"reflects the serious nature of the
OL,15,Fconcerns raised".
