OL,3,CCharity Commission launches inquiry
OL,4,Cinto Presbyterian Church
OL,6,FFrances McCandless, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe commission, said: "Safeguarding is
OL,8,Ffundamental to maintaining public
OL,9,Ftrust in charities. Every charity must
OL,10,Fmake the safety and wellbeing of those
OL,11,Fthey serve their highest priority."
OL,13,FThe PSNI previously launched an
OL,14,Finvestigation into the safeguarding
OL,15,Fconcerns.
OL,17,FAssistant Chief Constable Davy Beck
OL,18,Fadded: "We are aware of the
OL,19,Fannouncement by the Charity Commission
OL,20,Fregarding the opening of a statutory
OL,21,Finquiry.
