OL,6,F"As previously confirmed, the police
OL,7,Fservice has an ongoing investigation
OL,8,Finto safeguarding concerns connected
OL,9,Fto the Presbyterian Church in Ireland.
OL,10,FThis work remains active and will not
OL,11,Fbe affected by the Charity
OL,12,FCommission's inquiry processes.
OL,14,F"Safeguarding is a priority for the
OL,15,Fpolice service. We take any
OL,16,Finformation suggesting risk or
OL,17,Fpotential criminality extremely
OL,18,Fseriously.
